clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: Investigated for use treatment in osteoporosis A19388

contraindications.disease: Odanacatib was found to increase the risk of stroke A19388 No further toxicological studies have been performed
contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Increases bone mineral density and reduces risk of fractures in osteoporosis A19389
